Description_lang: Dealing damage with spells and abilities has a chance to apply a stack of Ever-Decaying Spores to your target. At 5 stacks the spores rapidly decay and inflict ${$s2*$407090d} Nature damage over $407090d.Sometimes the spores will immediately decay and inflict $s2 Nature damage to you.This effect is increased by $378758s2% if you equip an item crafted with a Toxified Armor Patch.
